   <indicator measure="5">
    <title>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">Results achieved</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">R&#xE9;sultats atteints</narrative>
    </title>
    <description>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">Results achieved as of the end of the project (March 2019) include: (1) successful clearance of 443,511 square meters of minefields; (2) the safe destruction of 2,674 anti-personnel mines and other unexploded remnants of war; and (3) employment for 115 local residents, of whom 48 (42%) were women. Overall, an estimated 30,000 women, men, girls and boys now have increased access to resettlement areas, public services, and livelihoods activities in former conflict areas of Northern Province, Sri Lanka.</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">R&#xE9;sultats obtenus &#xE0; la fin du projet (mars 2019) : 1) d&#xE9;minage r&#xE9;ussi de 443 511 m&#xE8;tres carr&#xE9;s de terrain min&#xE9;; 2) destruction s&#xE9;curitaire de 2 674 mines antipersonnel et autres munitions non explos&#xE9;es et; 3) cr&#xE9;ation de 115 emplois pour les r&#xE9;sidents locaux, dont 48 (42 %) pour des femmes. En tout, environ 30 000 femmes, hommes, filles et gar&#xE7;ons ont dor&#xE9;navant un acc&#xE8;s accru aux zones de r&#xE9;installation, aux services publics ainsi qu&#x2019;aux moyens de subsistance dans d&#x2019;anciennes zones de conflits de la province du Nord au Sri Lanka.</narrative>
    </description>
   </indicator>
  </result>
  <result type="2">
   <title>
    <narrative xml:lang="EN">Expected Results</narrative>
    <narrative xml:lang="FR">R&#xE9;sultats escompt&#xE9;s</narrative>
   </title>
   <indicator measure="5">
    <title>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">Results expected</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">R&#xE9;sultats escompt&#xE9;s</narrative>
    </title>
    <description>
     <narrative xml:lang="FR">Parmi les r&#xE9;sultats interm&#xE9;diaires escompt&#xE9;s du projet, mentionnons : 1) acc&#xE8;s accru &#xE0; la r&#xE9;installation des d&#xE9;plac&#xE9;s internes femmes, hommes et enfants;  2) acc&#xE8;s accru aux services publics de femmes, des hommes et des enfants  touch&#xE9;s par le conflit; 3) acc&#xE8;s accru aux possibilit&#xE9;s de moyens de subsistance pour les hommes et les femmes touch&#xE9;s par le conflit.</narrative>
     <narrative xml:lang="EN">The expected intermediate outcomes for this project include: 1) increased access to resettlement of internally displaced women, men and children; 2) increased access to public services by conflict-affected women, men and children; and, 3) increased access to livelihood opportunities for conflict-affected women and men.</narrative>
    </description>
   </indicator>
  </result>
